snippet.title: The Elder Scrolls: Legends - Isle of Madness Trailer
snippet.description:
Sheogorath is coming back to TESLegends with our upcoming Isle of Madness story expansion! Get all the details here: https://legends.bethesda.net/en/article/744U8w86v66KE2eqOMowce/prepare-yourself-for-isle-of-madness 

Pre-orders are now available!

Follow The Elder Scrolls: Legends on social media:
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/TESLegends
Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/TESLegends
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/TESLegends

ESRB RATING: TEEN with Violence and Blood.
